name: OTech Sample Kit : Metallization Inks
description:
Sample kit includes 4 samples of printed silver layers (electrodes) on different surfaces that showcase the variety of our inks. The samples included are:

1. Transparent layer on PET

2. Non-transparent reflective layer on PET

3. Non-transparent layer on fabric

4. Non-transparent layer on paper

The sample sizes are around 3.5 cm x 4.5 cm or similar.
